pull.title: Free icons
pull.body: This solves a lot of the copyright issues with LGPL'd Nuvola icons, but not all yet (a couple of them look hard to find replacements for, especially the animation).

events.message: Replace icons with Nuvola (LGPL 2.1): all non-free except for those by Wladimir van der Laan (who will hopefully relicense)
Replace icons with Nuvola (LGPL 2.1): some (but not all) GPL-licensed

events.body:
ACK, looks good enough.
Can you update doc/assets-attribution.txt with the new copyright as well?
(Or maybe remove the duplicated copyright file?)

Good replacements. 

The only one I don't like is the now 'home' icon, it's too crowded and 3-dimensional. I'd like a more simplified one that fits the blue-ish theme of the other tab icons. 

I'll do some searching too...
